ROBOT Sophia who looks like a real human being is on visit to Mzansi. Sophia wowed the audience which included pupils who were excited about a human like robot that can make conversations. The human like robot answered questions about the relevance of the arts in an era where so much focus is on Artificial Intelligence. She is Mzansi to attend the Davos of Human Capital conference where over 500 senior leaders and HR professionals from across Africa gathered. The one-day conference enables leaders to define the future for organizations in an era of artificial intelligence (AI) and digital disruption.  